longBusinessSummary: EVS Broadcast Equipment SA provides live video technology for broadcast and media productions worldwide. It offers replay and effects tools for exchange, review, transcoding, storytelling graphics, and collaboration; range of assets to ingest, create, and manage enhanced content; unified live production systems that enable live switching, create replays and highlights, control audio, create and insert graphics, and play back content; production switchers; and AI-based camera automation systems. The company also provides multi-camera review systems; range of live production servers; IP infrastructures; and media storage solutions. In addition, it offers support services, such as download area, support portal, and repository of products. The company offers solutions in the areas of live sports images, entertainment shows, and news content. EVS Broadcast Equipment SA was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Seraing, Belgium.
